[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "フロッケ",
		"romanized_name": "Flocke",
		"model_path_hash": "8444632684097041943",
		"text": "もうすっかり夜ですね……\nホルハーツ鳥、どこにいるんでしょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1324369732733195994",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "見つからないわね。\n湿原の奥まで来たけど、手掛かりもないし……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "おい、あそこ……誰か立ってるぞ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "フロッケ",
		"romanized_name": "Flocke",
		"model_path_hash": "8444632684097041943",
		"text": "シスターさん？　こんな場所に？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1324369732733195994",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "レースの参加者？\nでも、一人でいるのは変よね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "あらあら。迷える者が一人、二人……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "フロッケ",
		"romanized_name": "Flocke",
		"model_path_hash": "8444632684097041943",
		"text": "危ない！　魔物が……！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1324369732733195994",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "おい、助けに――",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "分かりました。\n存分に――“語り合い”ましょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "……安らかに",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "なに、今の……！？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "フロッケ",
		"romanized_name": "Flocke",
		"model_path_hash": "8444632684097041943",
		"text": "すごい……あんな大きな銃、初めて見ました",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1324369732733195994",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "あいつ、ただ者じゃねぇな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "こんばんは。\nお騒がせしてしまいましたね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……あんた、何者？　レースの参加者なの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "はい。会えてよかったです、ヴァレリアさん",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……私のこと、知ってるの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "もちろんです。\nあなたがたのことは、以前から聞き及んでおりますので",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "レースは一人じゃ参加できないはずだが……\n仲間とはぐれたのか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "いえ、仲間ならあなたがたの後ろにおりますよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "よっ、久しぶりだね、相棒っ、家族たち",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ハイディ！？　どうしてここに――",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "おいおい。家の事情とやらは片付いたのかよ！？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "まあ、ね。みんなに追いつこうとは思ってたけど、\nまさかこんな所で再会するなんて",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……とにかく、無事でよかったわ。\nやっぱり、あんたがいると心強いわね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "フロッケ",
		"romanized_name": "Flocke",
		"model_path_hash": "8444632684097041943",
		"text": "これでまた家族全員が揃いましたね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1324369732733195994",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "皆さんの絆、素敵です。\nハイディが話していた通りの、温かい方々ですね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "カロリン",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline",
		"model_path_hash": "5485149628928083359",
		"text": "私はカロリン・ヤスベルと申します。\n旅するシスターをしております。以後、お見知りおきを",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "旅するシスター、ね。道理で戦い慣れてると思ったわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "えげつねえ戦い方してたぜ。\n魔物に負ける心配はなさそうだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "それで……教えてくれるのよね？\n今までなにしてたか",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "……ああ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "ヴァレリアの相棒であり、家族。\nとある理由から別行動していた",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "カロリン・ヤスベル",
		"romanized_name": "Caroline Jasper",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ハイディの旧友で、シスター兼冒険者。\n研鑽を積むため、ハイディと共に行動している",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5434631736340677129",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]